            "term": 1,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Try these [classic Canadian recipes](https://canadianfoodfocus.org/in-your-kitchen/classic-canadian-dishes/) from the provinces you are studying. \n[ ] [This video](https://storymaps.arcgis.com/stories/95c8dfc9d1584d459e7e6c6f84422673) looks at how the cycle of the seasons affects the way we connect with the land, through the lenses of both the Métis and the Woodland Cree Nations."
          }
        ]
