          {
            "id": "recl2loc04x7CfVZY",
            "term": 2,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] View Arctic wildlife in[ this slideshow ](https://storymaps.arcgis.com/stories/ccf0ce17869b494683ec440b7d58ace4)from Canadian Geographic. \n[ ] [View this map ](https://canadaoceanmap.ca/#)of Canada's ocean and freshwater system."
